

    
       William Gillespie, who filled in as councilor for the class of '05 during the 2002-2003 school year, has been re-hired at the Prep for this upcoming school year. Gillespie spent the last year working as a councilor at Bishop Eustace Preparatory School in Pennsauken,New Jersey. Gillespie had also taught English to Pre-Eight grade students last summer. Those students will be entering the Prep as freshman this year.      
    
    
